we should be able to remove much of this code and * just override the relevant methods. * * Planner rule that reduces aggregate functions in * {@link org.apache.calcite.rel.core.Aggregate}s to simpler forms. * *

Rewrites: *

    * *
  • AVG(x) → SUM(x) / COUNT(x) * *
  • STDDEV_POP(x) → SQRT( * (SUM(x * x) - SUM(x) * SUM(x) / COUNT(x)) * / COUNT(x)) * *
  • STDDEV_SAMP(x) → SQRT( * (SUM(x * x) - SUM(x) * SUM(x) / COUNT(x)) * / CASE COUNT(x) WHEN 1 THEN NULL ELSE COUNT(x) - 1 END) * *
  • VAR_POP(x) → (SUM(x * x) - SUM(x) * SUM(x) / COUNT(x)) * / COUNT(x) * *
  • VAR_SAMP(x) → (SUM(x * x) - SUM(x) * SUM(x) / COUNT(x)) * / CASE COUNT(x) WHEN 1 THEN NULL ELSE COUNT(x) - 1 END *
*/

Any Managed tables may * be made insert-only transactional table.
